    <item>
      <title>Stora 首席执行官表示，该公司将投资 1 亿欧元用于木质电动汽车电池</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/stora-enso-hel-sterv-invests-in-lignin-ev-batteries-ceo-hans-sohlstrom-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据斯道拉恩索公司首席执行官称，该公司将投资约 1 亿欧元（1.1 亿美元）用于一项开创性项目，利用木材制造电动汽车电池，为目前在中国生产的零部件提供替代品]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/stora-enso-hel-sterv-invests-in-lignin-ev-batteries-ceo-hans-sohlstrom-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达斯称印度通胀正在以“非常”缓慢的速度缓和</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/india-s-inflation-moderating-at-a-very-slow-pace-das-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度储备银行行长沙克提坎塔·达斯周二表示，印度的通胀持续居高不下，因此央行讨论改变货币政策立场还为时过早。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/india-s-inflation-moderating-at-a-very-slow-pace-das-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:52:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>农林中央银行将出售 630 亿美元主权债券以减少损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/norinchukin-bank-to-sell-63-billion-of-bonds-to-stem-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本农业银行发言人表示，农林中央银行计划出售约 10 万亿日元（630 亿美元）的美国和欧洲主权债券，以弥补因错误押注利率而造成的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/norinchukin-bank-to-sell-63-billion-of-bonds-to-stem-losses</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:40:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求增长推动油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-18/oil-prices-moving-higher-as-demand-grows-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本月油价维持在最高点附近，全球市场风险偏好情绪推动原油价格近期上涨。随着夏季驾车季节的到来，汽油需求也在上升。彭博社的威尔·肯尼迪报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-18/oil-prices-moving-higher-as-demand-grows-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:39:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典的核电目标充满挑战但可以实现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/sweden-s-nuclear-power-goal-is-challenging-but-attainable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典政府的目标是在下一个十年中期实现新核电装机容量的上线，这是一个巨大的挑战，但据瑞典原子能复兴运动协调员称，这个目标是可以实现的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/sweden-s-nuclear-power-goal-is-challenging-but-attainable</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:27:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃达丰拟以高达 11 亿美元的价格出售 Indus Towers 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/vodafone-seeks-to-sell-indus-towers-stake-for-up-to-1-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博新闻社获得的交易条款，沃达丰集团 (Vodafone Group Plc) 正考虑通过大宗交易出售印度 Indus Towers Ltd. 9.94% 的股份，因为这家总部位于英国的运营商正在继续精简其投资组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/vodafone-seeks-to-sell-indus-towers-stake-for-up-to-1-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
