      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/hungary-slows-rate-cut-pace-toward-end-of-monetary-easing-cycle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利在货币宽松周期的一年多内福林贬值之后，放慢了降息步伐。]]></description>
